reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Sleek, and Compact, but has its flaws
reviews.reviewText: 3 settings. Low, cool, and bright light. Luckily the recharge cord that comes with the unit is long enough to reach to the floor where I can keep it plugged in at all times. Otherwise, the battery doesn't last long. The Pencil holder is nice, but don't put scissors or anything heavy in it or the light will fall over because there is no base to support this product properly. I had a temporary problem with the light turning on by itself. It did this for one day and then started working properly. I don't know why this happened. This light is not for a large surface desk. A medium or small desk is appropriate for this model (12 bulb). I've had this for a month, and I'm satisfied. I got what I paid for.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 3, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I love this little light but it starts to dim really quick, within 2 hrs it's dying. Luckily it works while it's plugged in so I just keep it plugged in most of the time, but that's annoying because I have to use an extension cord since I don't have an outlet near me. It's also top heavy, make sure you put some stuff in the pencil holder, otherwise it falls when the light is extended out. So, if you have an outlet and fill the pencil holder I think this is a great buy, but if you need a portable long lasting light you might want to look elsewhere
